%h2 Feedback Responses

%p
  Thank you for your time and input.  Here's what everyone had to say:

.responses
  %ul
    - @responses.each do |response|
      %li{:class => cycle('even','odd')}
        = link_to_function(responder(response), "$('q_and_a_#{response.id}').toggle()")
        %ul{:class => 'q_and_a', :id => "q_and_a_#{response.id}", :style => "display: none;"}
          = render :partial => 'answer', :collection => response.answers
